<div class="ui vertical stripe segment">
  <div class="ui middle aligned stackable grid container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="eight wide column">
        <h3 class="ui header">What is OrdrHub?</h3>
        <p>OrdrHub is a single application to manage all of your incoming orders across multiple ordering services. Simplify your staff's workflow today by using our intuitive platform that can run on any existing device with access to a web browser.</p>
        <h3 class="ui header">Why use OrdrHub?</h3>
        <p>Online ordering services are great for your business, but currently they each often require their own equipment causing incoming orders to be scattered and difficult to maintain. OrdrHub aggregates all of these orders into a simple-to-use platform so that you're spending your time efficiently.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="six wide right floated column">
        <%= image_tag 'ipad.png', class: 'ui big image' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="center aligned column">
        <button class="ui huge primary beta button">Set Up Now</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

